Effortlessly Save Your Browser Tabs as PDFs

Print All Tabs to PDF is a simple yet powerful Chrome extension that allows you to save all your open browser tabs as PDF files. Whether you need a single, combined PDF of all your tabs or separate PDFs for each one, this extension makes it quick and easy. Ideal for research, project documentation, or archiving web content, Print All Tabs to PDF helps you stay organized and efficient. Simply choose your mode, customize file names, and let the extension handle the rest. Save time and streamline your workflow with just a few clicks!
